                            <comment id="14455508" author="krosenvold" created="Fri, 9 Nov 2012 00:11:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I see this issue quite clearly in the code; the failure detection will ignore failures in the first provider fails. If you have made a small test project, please upload it and I will make an IT.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14455546" author="larrys" created="Fri, 9 Nov 2012 09:12:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is a test where JUnit fails, and TestNG passes. You can easily switch the asserts in each to flip it around so you can get two IT&apos;s out of it...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
